<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pure mathematics: we decide the destination, we look at the weather, the time to travel and the price. In this way, if we have our eyes on </span><a href="http://www.exteriores.gob.es/Portal/es/ServiciosAlCiudadano/SiViajasAlExtranjero/Paginas/DetalleRecomendacion.aspx?IdP=49" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><b>Costa Rica</b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> as our next holiday destination, we will check what to see, what places to visit, what the weather is like, what the </span><b>best time to travel to Costa Rica is</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, but also </span><b>how much these holidays will cost. </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">A price that can vary depending on whether you are going to organise it on your own or if you are going to leave it to the </span><a href="https://asuaire.com/viajes-a-costa-rica"><b>travel agency in Costa Rica</b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Let&#8217;s evaluate the price.</span></p>
<div id="toc_container" class="toc_light_blue no_bullets"><p class="toc_title">Contenido</p><ul class="toc_list"><li><ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul></li><li></li></ul></div>
<h2><span id="The_price_of_the_trip_with_a_travel_agency_in_Costa_Rica">The price of the trip with a travel agency in Costa Rica</span></h2>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21118" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21118" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hiring this type of trip with a <a href="https://asuaire.com/blog/en/costa-rica-en/top-activities-arenal-volcano">specialised agency</a>, such as </span><b>Asuaire Travel</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, is an advantages which starts with the best price we are trying to find. Having more than 20 years of experience is one of the advantages and therefore being able to get the most competitive prices.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">However, it is clear that the price of this trip will depend on what each traveller wants in terms of accommodation, visits or type of trip. However, it is interesting to know in general terms that </span><b>travelling to Costa Rica is not excessively expensive </b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> if we take into account the prices of meals, beverages, accommodations or transport. </span></p>
<h3><span id="The_typical_dishes_of_Costa_Rica_and_their_prices">The typical dishes of Costa Rica and their prices</span></h3>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21253" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21253" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Ceviche-02-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">An interesting fact, in addition to the references that we are going to give you regarding prices, is that </span><b>in Costa Rica you can use US dollars or colonos interchangeably. </b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> This is why, and taking into account the change, it will always be advisable to pay in dollars so as not to be subject to the fluctuation that affects the local currency. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">So, to give you a clear idea of how much a meal can cost you in Costa Rica you should know that in most food houses in the country you can </span><b>eat a set menu for about 8 or 10 dollars</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Including dessert and drink. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">The most typical Costa Rican establishments are called </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">sodas</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;">. </span><b>Eating a casado</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, one of the </span><a href="https://www.costaricatalk.com/es/blog-es/top-5-comidas-costa-rica?gclid=Cj0KCQjwhdTqBRDNARIsABsOl99ZZQbvNP_h3g-u0j7aa_GWCQIqvXdnLd5N2AQSRvgcLodALeHQFksaAiLoEALw_wcB" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><b>most typical dishes in Costa Rica</b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, in this type of establishment can cost you </span><b>about 7 dollars.  </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">However, here is a small list for you to get a better idea of the prices of typical dishes. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21120" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21120" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Gallo-pinto-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p><b>&#8211; Gallo pinto</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: between 4 and 5 dollars.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><b>&#8211; Chorreadas</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: maximum 3 dollars.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><b>&#8211; Olla de carne</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: about 3 dollars.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><b>&#8211; Chifrijo</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: between 5 and 7 dollars.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><b>&#8211; Ceviche</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: between 5 and 7 dollars.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span></p>
<h3><span id="The_price_of_transport">The price of transport</span></h3>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21126" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21126" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is interesting to consider these references especially when calculating how much your holiday can cost you in this destination. Why? It’s very simple. As it is a very small country, it is normal to get around by public transport so that you don’t miss out on seeing anything. </span><b>Let&#8217;s see how much these transports cost. </b><b><br />
</b><b><br />
</b><b>&#8211; Buses</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: they are cheap throughout the country if we consider that a trip, depending on the distance, can cost you between </span><b>0.20 and 0.70 dollars</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. There are other types of buses for longer journeys that can cost about 2 dollars. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20473" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20473" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Costa-Rica-con-niños-05-min-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></span><b>&#8211; Taxis</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: </span><b>they use a metre,</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> which means you can see the price of your trip. We have one tip regarding this: </span><b>ensure that when you get into the taxi the metre is not already on </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">and also ensure that it is not turned off.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><b>&#8211; Internal flights</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">: flying between cities and with flights that last less than an hour they are not very expensive. In this case we cannot give you an exact figure because, as with international flights, </span><b>the price varies</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> depending on many factors. We can only tell you that </span><b>they are not excessively expensive if you book them through a trusted agency</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> before arriving at the destination.</span></p>
<h3><span id="Other_expenses_to_plan_the_cost_of_your_holiday">Other expenses to plan the cost of your holiday</span></h3>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21129" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21129" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Tortuguero-05-min-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To complete this price plan for a trip to Costa Rica it must definitely be made clear that this will increase or decrease depending on what your plan is regarding </span><b>what to see in Costa Rica</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. So, for example, if you dare to go on an excursion to see the curious and </span><b>famous</b> <a href="https://cronicasargonauta.com/desove-de-tortugas-tortuguero-costa-rica/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><b>turtle nesting</b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, you must take into account the price of these types of activities. This is priced at about </span><b>$ 30</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span></p>
<h2><span id="Everything_is_easier_with_a_travel_agency_in_Costa_Rica">Everything is easier with a travel agency in Costa Rica</span></h2>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21124" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20675'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" data-lazy-srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-600x338.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz.jpg" /><noscript><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-21124" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" title="" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz.jpg 1200w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/gente-feliz-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Although prices are affordable, if we start adding everything you will need to book a perfect trip on your own, the amount can end up being more than you imagined. It will always be more expensive than opting for the packages offered by a good </span><b>travel agency in Costa Rica</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> like </span><b>Asuaire</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. The specialisation and volumes of travellers they work with explain why you will have a better trip for a much lower price. It is a simple equation to which the fact of not having to do the math or go through any trouble during the journey can be added.  </span></p>
		</div>

